Content: <@!152566937442975744>_ ARC is a team of members comprised by the moderating team who have been chosen to represent the opinions of the users of the r/teenagers user-base. ARC is comprised of three branches_ Discord_ Reddit and TGN. Users should feel free to come to ARC members to help them implement changes and make their voices feel heard. Each ARC's term is 60 days.
